---
title: Savoury Rib Dinner with Loaded Baked Potatoes
description: BBQ ribs, loaded baked potatoes and cheesy topped broccoli make for a show-stopping, crowd-pleasing meal. Where to dig in first is going to be the hardest part of tonight's dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cotes-levees-savoureuses-2a511b9d.jpg
